---
title: Maple-Mustard Glazed Chicken Breasts with BBQ-Spiced Wedges and Green Beans
description: You can't go wrong with classic Canadian flavours like maple and mustard! Potato wedges get tossed in BBQ Seasoning for added smokiness to complement the sweetness from the maple syrup.
